  "description": "MUST activate before writing/editing/deleting any class/id/function. 43 commands. v5.10: Dart/Flutter parser (classes, enums, mixins, extensions, widgets, Riverpod providers, AutoRoute), NestJS framework detection + @Controller/@Get/@Post route extraction, Flutter framework detection (pubspec.yaml), Express/Fastify framework detection, Docker/containerization detection, CI/CD pipeline detection (GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, Jenkins, etc.), SQL file discovery, Dart outline engine. v5.8: Rust framework detection, Rust HTTP route extraction, Cargo workspace, is_generated_file, state-map __dunder filtering, smell health_score. Agent-optimized: score-based ask routing, markdown formatters, semantic conventions, AGENT.md, decision trees, quality metrics. TSX backend extraction. Fuzzy file lookup. Auto-incremental scan. Shared utils. Proper logging. 13+ langs (JS/TS/Rust/Python/Vue/Svelte/Dart/C++/Go/Tailwind/HTML). Workspace auto-detect. Tested on immich-app/immich (2760 files: TS+Svelte+Dart+Python polyglot), denoland/deno (5400+ Rust+TS), elizaOS/eliza (5300+ AI agent).",
